    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines a profile for the Autonomous System Provider
   Authorization (ASPA) object in the Resource Public Key Infrastructure
   (RPKI).  An ASPA is a digitally signed object that provides a means
   of validating that a Customer Autonomous System (CAS) has authorized
   the members of a specified Provider AS set as its upstream
   provider(s) and/or connected Internet-exchange route server(s).


	 </t>
